data.description: This stunning home in immaculate conditions, is the perfect place to relax and unwind. Located in the desirable Sterling on the lake neighborhood. As you step into the entry way you have beautiful tile floors covering the office/sitting room area leading to wood floors in the family room, the kitchen overlooking the family room boast tile floors with stain cabinets and Corian countertops. There's a bonus room on the main that can serve as a 4th bedroom/Guest room, As you walk upstairs you have a loft, two large rooms with wood floors. The oversized master has wood floors, the master bath has his and hers, tile floors, tile backsplash with jacuzzi tub and a customize walk in closet.. A must see.. Customized Laundry room, walk outside to a recently painted fenced backyard with portable covered patio that will stay with the property. The property has a irrigation system that will keep your grass fed yearly. The Sterling on the Lake neighborhood offers a variety of amenities, including a clubhouse with fitness center, library, and movie theater, tennis courts, pickleball courts, playground, award-winning treehouse, community pool with waterslide, separate lap pool, and walking trails. Love fishing? The lake is stocked - two or three pound bass isn't uncommon! If fishing isn't your thing, take your canoe for a spin to the picnic island. There's also a public library and cafe at the entrance the neighborhood! Target, TJMAXX, Home Depot, Publix, and many more shops are located close by. Flowery Branch offers even more shopping and dining. Schedule your showing today!
